sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>TCP TLS(opt)
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant LMPod as LMEval Pod<br/>+ Driver 5000/TCP
    participant HFHub as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 / OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Client as Client
    participant GORCHProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS
    participant Orchestrator as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS
    participant Detector as Detector InferenceService
    participant GenSvc as Generation InferenceService

    rect rgb(220, 235, 255)
        Note over User, DB: Flow 1: TrustyAI Model Explainability
        User->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token
        Route->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+ (serving cert)
        KRBAC->>KRBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(get services)
        KRBAC->>TAS: HTTP/8080<br/>localhost (no TLS)
        TAS->>DB: TCP (configurable)<br/>TLS optional, Username/Password
        DB-->>TAS: Query Results
        TAS-->>KRBAC: Response
        KRBAC-->>Route: HTTPS Response
        Route-->>User: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over KServe, DB: Flow 2: KServe Payload Processing
        KServe->>TAS: HTTP/8080<br/>Payload data (no auth)
        TAS->>DB: Store payload<br/>PVC or PostgreSQL
        DB-->>TAS: Stored
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over User, S3: Flow 3: LM Evaluation Job Execution
        User->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token<br/>Create LMEvalJob CR
        K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Watch event
        LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>SA Token<br/>Create Pod
        K8sAPI-->>LMPod: Pod scheduled
        Note over LMPod: Init container copies<br/>driver binary to shared volume
        LMESCtrl->>LMPod: HTTP/5000<br/>Pod exec (status)
        LMPod->>HFHub: HTTPS/443<br/>API Token<br/>Download model/dataset
        HFHub-->>LMPod: Model artifacts
        LMPod->>S3: HTTPS/443<br/>AWS IAM / Username<br/>Upload results
        S3-->>LMPod: Stored
        LMPod-->>LMESCtrl: Job complete
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
        Note over Client, GenSvc: Flow 4: Guardrails Orchestration
        Client->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token
        Route->>GORCHProxy: HTTPS/8432<br/>TLS 1.2+
        GORCHProxy->>GORCHProxy: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(get services)
        GORCHProxy->>Orchestrator: HTTPS/8032<br/>TLS 1.2+ (serving cert)
        Orchestrator->>Detector: HTTP(S) varies<br/>TLS if configured
        Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection result
        Orchestrator->>GenSvc: HTTP(S) varies<br/>TLS if configured
        GenSvc-->>Orchestrator: Generated response
        Orchestrator-->>GORCHProxy: Guarded response
        GORCHProxy-->>Route: HTTPS Response
        Route-->>Client: JSON Response
    end
